modules.description: Defines a time-based axis configuration for real-time data visualization. It specializes in streaming time-series data, enabling dynamic updates aligned with Chart.js's time axis requirements. Useful for displaying live sensor readings or log data with timestamps.

This module configures real-time data streaming for Chart.js charts, focusing on time-based axes. It provides functions to create and apply streaming configurations to chart axes and global settings, specifically for handling live time-series data like sensor inputs or log streams. Key operations include setting up streaming parameters, binding them to chart options or axes, and retrieving existing configurations.
